# Intito MasterFlow import JSON parent-child
# Purpose: Import parent-child JSON payloads into a managed dimension or work version.
# Sources:
# - Source JSON payload
# - Managed master dimension or selected work version
# Parameters:
# - pPrefix: Naming prefix for Intito MasterFlow control objects. Default 'IMF'.
# - pDimensionCode: Managed dimension code.
# - pVersionId: Optional work version.
# - pFilePath: Source file path.
# Prolog:
# - Resolve whether import target is master or work version.
# Metadata:
# - Determine JSON hierarchy schema and target field mapping.
# Data:
# - Read JSON parent-child rows and apply structural updates.
# Epilog:
# - Leave the target dimension updated and ready for validation.

sPrefix = Trim(pPrefix);
If(sPrefix @= '');
  sPrefix = 'IMF';
EndIf;

